ed="T" n="0716a18"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0716a18"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06"><name>唐</name></date><placeName key="PL000000023581">洛京</placeName><persName key="A008859">智慧</persName>傳<ptr target="#n216"/></head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0716a19"/><persName key="A008859">釋智慧</persName>者，<name>梵</name>名<persName key="A008859">般剌若</persName>也，姓<name>憍答摩</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000000056">北<lb
ed="T" n="0716a20"/>天竺迦畢試國</placeName>人。穎悟天資。<date key="j19913391991704" from-iso="+0740-01-01" to-iso="+0740-12-31">七歲</date><ptr target="#n240"/>發心，違侍<lb
ed="T" n="0716a21"/>二親，歸依三寶。時從大德<persName key="A008860">調伏軍</persName>教誦《四阿<lb
ed="T" n="0716a22"/>含》，滿十萬頌，《阿毘達磨》三萬頌。及年應法，<lb
ed="T" n="0716a23"/>隨<ref target="#A008860" type="person">師</ref>往別國<ptr target="#n243"/>，納具足戒。誦《薩婆多》<ptr type="glossary" target="#g244"/>近四萬<lb
ed="T" n="0716a24"/>頌，《俱舍》二萬八千頌，又誦《大婆沙》，兼通其<lb
ed="T" n="0716a25"/>義<ptr target="#n217"/>。七年於<ref target="#PL000000055417" type="place">彼</ref>專習小乘。後<ptr target="#n245"/>詣<placeName key="PL000000048272">中天竺那爛<lb
ed="T" n="0716a26"/>陀寺</placeName>，稟學大乘《唯識》、《瑜伽》、《中邊》等論、《金剛般<lb
ed="T" n="0716a27"/>若經》、「因明」、「聲明」、「醫明」<ptr type="glossary" target="#g88"/>、<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>王</sic><corr>工</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="beg0716sgsz5"/>律<anchor xml:id="end0716sgsz5"/>論<ptr target="#n247"/>等，並依承<persName key="A008861">智護</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0716a28"/><persName key="A008862">進友</persName>、<persName key="A008863">智友</persName>三大論師。復遊<placeName key="PL000000048391">雙林</placeName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g5"/>，經<placeName key="PLG00000000054">八塔</placeName>。往<lb
ed="T" n="0716a29"/>來瞻<anchor xml:id="beg0716sgsz6"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0716sgsz6"/>十有八年。聞<placeName key="PL000000048209">南<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>北</sic><corr>天</corr></choice>竺</placeName><ptr target="#n248"/>頗尚「持明」<ptr type="glossary" target="#g249"/>，遂往<pb ed="T" n="0716b" xml:id="T50.2061.0716b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0716b01"/>諮稟。<ref target="#PL000000048209" type="place">彼</ref>有灌頂<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g97"/>師名<persName key="A008864">達摩耶舍</persName>見<persName key="A008859">慧</persName>勤重<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g250"/><lb
ed="T" n="0716b02"/>可教，授瑜伽法、入曼荼羅、三密、護身、五部、印<lb
ed="T" n="0716b03"/>契經，于一年誦徹三千五百餘頌。</p><p>常聞<placeName key="PL000000000083"><anchor xml:id="beg0716sgsz8"/>支<anchor xml:id="end0716sgsz8"/>那<lb
ed="T" n="0716b04"/>大國</placeName>，<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>在中，錫指<ref target="#PL000000000083" type="place">東方</ref>，誓傳佛教。乃泛<lb
ed="T" n="0716b05"/>海東邁，垂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g251"/>至<placeName key="PL000000030464">廣州</placeName>，風飄却返，抵<placeName key="PL000000048734">執師子國</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0716b06"/>之東。又集資糧，重修巨舶，遍歷<placeName key="PL000000000153">南海</placeName>諸國。<lb
ed="T" n="0716b07"/>二十二年<ptr target="#n252"/>，再近<placeName key="PL000000030482">番禺</placeName>，風濤遽作，舶破人沒，唯<lb
ed="T" n="0716b08"/><persName key="A008859">慧</persName>存焉。夜至五更，其風方止，所齎經論，莫<lb
ed="T" n="0716b09"/>知所之。及登海壖<ptr type="glossary" target="#g253"/>，其夾<anchor xml:id="beg0716002"/>策<anchor xml:id="end0716002"/>已在岸矣，於<lb
ed="T" n="0716b10"/>白<anchor xml:id="beg0716003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>抄</sic><corr>沙</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0716003"/>內大竹筩中得之，宛為鬼物扶持而<lb
ed="T" n="0716b11"/>到。乃歎曰：「此《大乘理趣》<ptr target="#n14"/>等經，想<placeName key="PL000000000083"><anchor xml:id="beg0716sgsz10"/>支那<anchor xml:id="end0716sgsz10"/></placeName>人根熟<lb
ed="T" n="0716b12"/>矣！」</p><p>遂東北行，半月達<placeName key="PL000000030464">廣州</placeName>，即<persName key="A004215">德宗</persName><date notBefore-iso="+0780-02-15" key="j20059942006355" notAfter-iso="+0781-02-10"><name><name>建中</name></name>初</date><ptr target="#n254"/>也。<lb
ed="T" n="0716b13"/>屬<ref target="#A004215" type="person">帝</ref>違難<placeName key="PL000000043115">奉天</placeName><ptr target="#n255"/>，<date key="j20081792008532" from-iso="+0786-02-08" to-iso="+0787-01-27"><name>貞元</name>二年</date>始屆<ref target="#PL000000042189" type="place">京輦</ref>。見鄉<lb
ed="T" n="0716b14"/>親神策軍<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g256"/>正將<persName key="A008867">羅好心</persName>，即<persName key="A008859">慧</persName>舅氏之子也，悲<lb
ed="T" n="0716b15"/>喜相慰。將至家中，延留供養<ptr target="#n17"/>。<date key="j20103632010746" from-iso="+0792-02-01" to-iso="+0793-02-18">八年</date><ptr target="#n257"/>，上表舉<lb
ed="T" n="0716b16"/><persName key="A008859">慧</persName>翻傳，有勅令<ref target="#PL000000042189" type="place">京城</ref>諸寺大德名業殊眾者<lb
ed="T" n="0716b17"/>同譯，得<placeName key="PL000000055418">罽賓</placeName>三<anchor xml:id="beg0716sgsz11"/>藏<anchor xml:id="end0716sgsz11"/><persName key="A000993">般若</persName><ptr target="#n18"/>開釋<name>梵</name>本，翰林待<lb
ed="T" n="0716b18"/>詔<placeName key="PL000000042151">光宅寺</placeName>沙門<persName key="A000454">利言</persName>度語<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g109"/>，<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明寺</placeName>沙門<persName key="A001417">圓照</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0716b19"/>筆受<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g53"/>，<placeName key="PL000000042260">資聖寺</placeName><persName key="A001531">道液</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明寺</placeName><persName key="A008873">良秀</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000042412">莊嚴寺</placeName><persName key="A000214">應真</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0716b20"/><placeName key="PL000000042317">醴泉寺</placeName><persName key="A008875">超悟</persName>、<persName key="A000215">道岸</persName>、<persName key="A008877">辯空</persName>，並充證義<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g54"/>。<date key="j20105182010518" when-iso="+0792-07-05">六月八日</date><lb
ed="T" n="0716b21"/>欲剏經題<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g259"/>，勅右<anchor xml:id="beg0716sgsz12"/>街<anchor xml:id="end0716sgsz12"/>功德使<persName key="A008878">王希遷</persName>與右神<lb
ed="T" n="0716b22"/>策軍大將軍王<ptr target="#n260"/><persName key="A008879">孟涉</persName>、驃騎大將軍<persName key="A008880">馬有隣</persName>等<lb
ed="T" n="0716b23"/>送<name>梵</name>經出內。緇伍威儀<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g261"/>樂部相間，士女觀<lb
ed="T" n="0716b24"/>望，車騎交駢，迎入<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明寺</placeName>翻譯。即日賜錢<lb
ed="T" n="0716b25"/>一千貫<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g262"/>、<anchor xml:id="beg0716004"/>茶<anchor xml:id="end0716004"/>三十丳<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g263"/>、香一大合<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g264"/>，充其供施。開<lb
ed="T" n="0716b26"/>名題曰《大乘理趣六波羅蜜多經》，成十卷。<lb
ed="T" n="0716b27"/>又《華嚴長者問佛那羅延力經》、《般若心經》各<lb
ed="T" n="0716b28"/>一卷，皆<date key="j20103632010746" from-iso="+0792-02-01" to-iso="+0793-02-18"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0716sgsz13"/>貞<anchor xml:id="end0716sgsz13"/>元</name>八年</date><ptr target="#n265"/>所譯也。是歲<date from-iso="+0792-10-25" key="j20106302010658" to-iso="+0792-11-22">十月</date>繕寫畢。<lb
ed="T" n="0716b29"/><date key="j20106572010657" when-iso="+0792-11-21">二十八日</date>設綵車，大備威儀，引入<placeName key="PL000000042359">光順門</placeName>，<pb ed="T" n="0716c" xml:id="T50.2061.0716c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0716c01"/>進<ref target="#A004215" type="person">帝</ref>覽，忻然，慰勞勤至。勅於神策軍賜齋<lb
ed="T" n="0716c02"/>食，䞋<persName key="A008859">慧</persName>絹五百匹、冬服一副，餘人賜各有<lb
ed="T" n="0716c03"/>差。<persName key="A008859">慧</persName>表謝，答詔褒美。同日請譯經，<placeName key="PL000000043115">奉天</placeName>定<lb
ed="T" n="0716c04"/>難功臣<ptr target="#n266"/>開府儀同三司檢校太子詹事<persName key="A008867">羅好<lb
ed="T" n="0716c05"/>心</persName>上表云：「<ref target="#A008867" type="person">臣</ref>表弟沙門<persName key="A008859">般剌若</persName>先進《大乘理<lb
ed="T" n="0716c06"/>趣六波羅蜜》<name>梵</name>本經，伏奉<date key="j20104702010470" when-iso="+0792-05-18">今年四月十九日</date><lb
ed="T" n="0716c07"/>勅令<persName key="A008878">王希遷</persName>精選有道行僧於<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明寺</placeName>翻<lb
ed="T" n="0716c08"/>譯。今經帙已終，同詣<placeName key="PL000000042359">光順門</placeName>進<ref target="#A004215" type="person">上</ref>。」答詔云：「<lb
ed="T" n="0716c09"/><ref target="#A008867" type="person">卿</ref>之<ref target="#A008859" type="person">表弟</ref>早悟大乘，遠自<ref target="#PL000000048207" type="place">西方</ref>，<anchor xml:id="beg0716sgsz14"/>求<anchor xml:id="end0716sgsz14"/>遊<ref target="#PL000000000083" type="place">上國</ref>。<lb
ed="T" n="0716c10"/>宣六根<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g267"/>之奧義，演<placeName key="PL000000048391">雙樹</placeName>之微言。念以精誠<lb
ed="T" n="0716c11"/>所宜欽重，是令翻譯，俾用流行。<ref target="#A008867" type="person">卿</ref>夙慕忠<lb
ed="T" n="0716c12"/>勤，職<anchor xml:id="beg0716sgsz15"/>司<anchor xml:id="end0716sgsz15"/>禁衛，省覽表疏，具見乃懷，所謝<lb
ed="T" n="0716c13"/>知。」<ptr target="#n268"/><persName key="A008867">好心</persName>以<persName key="A008866">朱泚</persName>圍逼之際，頗有戰功，預其<lb
ed="T" n="0716c14"/>中兵<ptr type="glossary" target="#g269"/>，為<ref target="#A004215" type="person">帝</ref>寵重。<persName key="A008859">慧</persName>得<persName key="A008867">好心</persName>啟導，譯務有光，<lb
ed="T" n="0716c15"/><ref target="#A004215" type="person">帝</ref>製《經序》<ptr target="#n270"/>焉。<persName key="A008859">慧</persName>後終于<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛陽</placeName>，葬<placeName key="PL000000023647">龍門</placeName>之<placeName key="PL000000023648">西<lb
ed="T" n="0716c16"/>岡</placeName>，塔今存矣。</p>
